    <p class="clause">D. The <b>Kunnamangalam Grama Panchayath</b> has granted the Site Approval and
    Building Permit No.BP/24094/2026 dated 12/02/2026 for the proposed construction of
    multistoried residential apartment building and the same is valid and subsisting as on
