    <p class="clause">(viii)&#160;The Promoter confirms that the Promoter is not restricted in any manner
    whatsoever from selling the said (apartment/plot) to the Allottee/s in the manner
    contemplated in this Agreement&#8217;.</p>

    <p class="clause">(ix)&#160;&#160;At the time of execution of the conveyance deed the Promoter shall handover
